<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbe0c6ffc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7385a"><num value="7385a">§ 7385a.</num><heading> Subrogation of the United States</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Upon payment of compensation under this subchapter, the United States is subrogated for the amount of the payment to a right or claim that the individual to whom the payment was made may have against any person on account of injuries referred to in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s7385">section 7385 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbe0c6ffd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/398/s1/dC/tXXXVI/s3642">Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [div. C, title XXXVI, § 3642]</ref>, <date date="2000-10-30">Oct. 30, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/1654">114 Stat. 1654</ref>, 1654A–509; <ref href="/us/pl/108/375/dC/tXXXI/s3162/b">Pub. L. 108–375, div. C, title XXXI, § 3162(b)</ref>, <date date="2004-10-28">Oct. 28, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/2186">118 Stat. 2186</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
